                    "R2aExhibit": {
                        "ProjectMissionDescription": {
                            "val": "The ADL Initiative collaborates with the DoD, the Federal government, Industry, and Academia partners to shape the way people learn, grow, and perform. The ADL\nProgram provides DoD, other Federal agencies, and international partners with innovative: (1) standards for training and education software, systems, and associated\nWeb services that demonstrate the \u201cart of the possible;\u201d (2) prototypes and proofs of concept that harness the power of learning technologies, such as computer\/\nWeb-based training, serious games, The ADL Initiative collaborates with the DoD, the Federal government, Industry, and Academia partners to shape the way people\nlearn, grow, and perform."
                        },
