                                    "Description": {
                                        "val": "ADL serves as the thought-leader for the DoD and other government agencies for learning science and learning\ntechnologies, enabling innovation, finding efficiencies, guiding customers into the future, and creating a shared vision and strategy for ADL\u2019s partners."
